gckanbun
================================================

Version: 2.0.0
Date: 2025-11-04
Author of Original ver.: Munehiro Yamamoto
Author of Modified ver.: Kosei Kawaguchi a.k.a. KKTeX
License: MIT

Description:
------------
This package provides a comprehensive set of commands required for typesetting classical Chinese texts in Japanese style.

Munehiro Yamamoto, the author of the original, generously granted permission to release this modified version.

Dependencies:
-------------
luatex-ja (If you don't use jlreq class, you MUST load luatex-ja package in advance.)

